lead_paragraph: U.S. Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton has postponed a trip planned for Sunday to Charlotte, North Carolina, which has seen sometimes violent protests after a black man was killed by police earlier this week.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Postpones Trip to Charlotte - Campaign Statement
